permisseons(tuyltvutyunner), vim((vi improved(vi-n barelavvel e)) text editor(textayin xmbagir))

1.
.1.
 sudo apt install vim
apt install -  apt install-y linux henc konkret ubuntu-um package(patet)-neri patetneri install anelu hamar e 


vim-i keyboard tricks

yy  - toxna copy anum, y(yank)
p   - pasta anum
u   - mi hat heta gnum, u(undo(hetarkel))
e   - bari verji taric bar bar heta gnum aysinqn dsax
w   - bari skzbi taric bar bar heta gnum aysinqn dsax
b   - bari skzbi taric bar bar araja gnum aysinqn aj
gg  - galisa fayli skizb
G kam shift+g  - fayli verja gnum
dd   - toxy jnjuma

h  - mi hat dsaxa gnum
j  - mi hat nerqeva gnum
k  - mi hat vereva gnum
l  - mi hat aja gnum

o kam O - mangamic poxancume insert rejim ev nor tox e bacum anmijapes cursoric mi hat nerqev

cc - toxy jnjuma ev mtnuma insert rejim, isk visual 3 rejimneric mer nshacsy jnjuma ev mtnuma insert rejim

esc  -  het e galis command mode(hramani rejim)
i    - mtnum e insert rejim
v    - mtnum e visual rejim
V kam shift+v   - mtnum e ayspes asacs visual line rejim ev baci da es cankacacs gorcsoxutyun ditarkelu em tox ar tox, ev ayntex vortex coursorn e ayd toxy avtomat nshvum e amboxjutyamb, hima stex menq karox enq vimin poxancel inch vor hraman voch te hramanayin rejimov ayl stexneri mijocov voroncic meky klini jnjel ays erku toxy jnjelu hamar sexmum en (d) tary 

ctrl+v   - mtnum e ayspes asacs visual block rejim
ystex sharjvume blok ar blok aysinqn vortex vor coursorn e aydtexic ete mi hat aj tanenq u mi hat nerqev knshvi et toxi ev nerqevi toxi hamapatasxan erku tarery






.2.
vim-y uni 3 ashxatanqayin rejim

.2.1. command mode(hramanayin rejim) - sa ayn rejimn e vor duq karoxanum eq hraman tal henc vim-in, hramannery irenic nerkayacnum en pahpanel faylery inch vor fayli nersum kam kam vim-i nersum gtnvelov inch vor mek ayl fayli parnakutyun bacel kardalu kam edit(xmbagrel) anelu hamar
aysinqn command mode-um menq hnaravorutyun unenq vim-in poxancel hramanner u hramannery poxancum enq kam command mode mtnum enq hamapatasxanabar es : erku ket u inch vor hramani anun havaqelov

:q  - q(quit(toxnel,lqel), :q -n durs e galis vimic
:w  - w(write(grel)), ete popoxutyun enq anum u uzum enq popoxutyuny pahpanel :w hramani mijocov enq anum, :w -n save(pahpanel) e anum

ete popoxutyunes anum u aran save anelu uzumes durs gas aysinqn anes :q beruma
E37: No write since last change (add ! to override) 
:q!  - durs e galis aranc popoxutyunnery faylum pahelu

.2.2.
visual mode(tesoxakan rejim) - aysinqn stex vim-um gtnvox fayli het voch mi xmbagrakan gorcsoxutyunner chenq anum ayl hnaravorutyun uneq orinak nshel inch vor mi text-i ktor texapoxutyun anel mek ayl fayl ev ayln ev ayln
aysinq visual mode-um hishum enq vor teqst havaqelu ashxatanq vorpes aydpisin chi katarvum

v  - mtnum e visual rejim
aysinqn cankacacs ban vor menq anenq ays rejimum vim-y yndunelu e vorpes visual(tesoxakan) rejim katarvox ban
hima ete menq aj dsax anenq mer cursore-i gtnvelu vayric mnacacs hatvacsnery sksum e nshely

visual line mode(tesoxakan gcsayin rejim)
V kam shift+v - mtnum e ayspes asacs visual line rejim
ev baci da es cankacacs gorcsoxutyun ditarkelu em tox ar tox, ev ayntex vortex coursorn e ayd toxy avtomat nshvum e amboxjutyamb, hima stex menq karox enq vimin poxancel inch vor hraman voch te hramanayin rejimov ayl stexneri mijocov voroncic meky klini jnjel ays erku toxy jnjelu hamar sexmum en (d) tary

visual block mode(tesoxakan blokayin rejim)
ctrl+v - mtnum e ayspes asacs visual block rejim 
ystex sharjvume blok ar blok aysinqn vortex vor coursorn e aydtexic ete mi hat aj tanenq u mi hat nerqev knshvi et toxi ev nerqevi toxi hamapatasxan erku tarery

visual,visual line,visual block rejumnerum  cc -n jnjuma nshvacsy ev ancnuma insert rejim aydtex grelov inch vor uzum eq ev ESC sxmelov ayn inch vor nshel eiq kpoxarinvi dser gracsov



.2.3.
insert mode(texadrman,mutqagrman rejim) - teqst havaqelu ashxatanq katarvum e insert mode-um

i  - mtnum e insert rejim


2.
nano - text editor(textayin xmbagir), ctrl + x -ov dursa galis


3.
Permissions(tuyltvutyunner)  -  -rwx rwx rwx
permission -nery 3 masi en bashanvum  read(kardal), write(grel), execute(katarel)

.1.
-  - regular file(sovorakan file)
d  - directory
l  - soft(symbolic) link
hradlinki demy eli gcsika(-)

c  - character file, xosqy gnum e sarqeri masin kam hatuk tesaki fayleri masin voronq ashxatum en bayteri hosqeri het, aysinqn menq inch vor informacia poxancum enq simvol ar simvol aysinqn hosqov, nman fayli orinak e /dev/null
ls -l /dev/null
crw-rw-rw- 1 root root 1, 3 Մար 25 11:03 /dev/null

b  - block file, sa en sarqeri kam en fayleri masin e xosqy gnum voronq ashxatum en voch te tvyalneri hosqeri het ayl tvyalneri amboxjakan ktorneri het blovk-eri het 


.2.
linux um qani tesaki ogtagorcsoxner en dasakargvum, aysinqn goyutyun uni ogtagorcsoxi inch vor tesak haskacoxutyun u sa chi veraberum administratori kam voch administratori sa veraberum e ira henc bnuytov tesakin te ov e fayli het ashxatoxyete ushadrutyun dardsneq en mardy ov fayly stexcsel e et mardy henc handisanuma  et fayli tery ayspes kochvacs owner(sepakanater)-y, aysinqn ete ogatagorcsoxy et fayly chi stexcel ogtagorcsoxy et fayli owner-y chi

-rw-rw-r-- 1 ubuntu ubuntu 4743 Մար 25 11:14 l6
araji ubuntu grvacsy bary ays depqum araji ubuntu grvacsy cuyc et alis e te ova ays l6 fayli owner-y (aysinqn vor usern e stexcsel l6 fayly
karox en linel urish userner
erkrod ubuntu grvacsy fayli xmbi anun e 



linux ashxarhum taranjatum enq 
owner(sepakanater), group(xumb), others(ayloq)
aysinqn ereq tesaki kam ereq xmbi ogtagorcsoxner kan

owner(sepakanater)  -  owner-y ayn usern e vory ayd fayli kam directory-i terne

group(xumb)  -  linux-um goyutyun uni xumb haskacoxutyun, vory teskanoren ansahmanapak qanakov karox e goyutyun unenal hamakragum vory irenic nerkayacnum e mi qani ogtagorcsoxneri xumb 
aysinqn ete duq linux hamakargy ogtagorcsum eq voch te miaynak ayl mi qani ogtagorcsoxner ogtvum en nuyn hamakargic duq yuraqanchyur ogtagorcsoxi hamar stexcsum eq ira arandsin txtapanaky home dir-um ira hamar tuylatvutyunneri inch vor shem eq sahmanum ev ayln ev ayln, aysinqn tarber ogtagorcsoxner patkeracreq 4-5 hogi ogtvum en ays nuyn hamakargic kam njyn hamakargchic vorosh ogtagorcsoxner, vorosh ogtagorcsoxner karox en patkanal mi xmbi nuyn xmbin

es vorpes ogtagorcsox inch vor mi xmbi mejem gtnvum 
ete es uzum em imanam te vor xmbum em gtnvum aysinqn en ogtagorcsoxy vor hima ogtagorcsum e, groups hramany inds kasi te es inch xmberi em patkanum, aysinqn sranq en bolor en xmberi anunnern en voronc mas em es 
ubuntu xumby avtomat stexcsvel e ays user-y stexcselis

ubuntu@ubuntu:/$ whoami
ubuntu
ubuntu@ubuntu:/$ groups
ubuntu adm cdrom sudo dip plugdev lpadmin lxd sambashare
ubuntu@ubuntu:/$ 


others(ayloq)  - faylin karox en mutq unenal ays 3 tesaki mardik, mard ov stexcsela ayd fayly aysinqn fayli owner(sepakanater)-y, mard vor inch vor xmbia patkanum u et xmbi hamar tuyltvutyun ka kam chka inch vor ban ogtagorcselu ev hamapatasxanabar ayloq aysinqn ayl ogtagorcsoxner voronq voch et xmbum en gtnvum voch asenq chgitem inch vor mi kapov aknhayt et ogtagorcsoxi het kap unen 


aysinqn yuraqanchyur fayli tesankyunic 3 tesaki ogtagorcsoxnern en ir het ashxatum 
-rw-rw-r-- 1 ubuntu ubuntu 4743 Մար 25 11:14 l6

owner   - araji ubuntu grvacsy bary ays depqum araji ubuntu grvacsy cuyc e talis e te ova ays l6 fayli owner-y (aysinqn vor usern e stexcsel l6 fayly
karox en linel urish userner

group   - erkrod ubuntu grvacsy fayli group(xumb)-i anunn e, aysiqn es ogtagorcsoxy patkanum e fayli xmbin aysinqn es fayly stexcsvacs e tulyatvutyamb kam es fayly patkanum e es inch xmbin apa es 2rd eryaky nshum e te et xmbin patkanox user-y inch accses(mutq) uni es hamapatasxan faylin, aysinq  cankacacs user vor patkanum e es xmbin et permission-nery kunena 

others   - u ete goutyun uni ogtagorcsox vory owner-y chi fayli, fayli hamapatasxanabar xmbum chi gtnvum apa et ogtagorcsoxy kkochvi other(ayl), et et user-i hamar ayspes asacs otar user-i hamar permission-nery hamapatasxanabar sahmanvum en verjin eryakov aysinqn eli nuyn skzbunqov
ete r-n ka apa read accses(mutq) uni
ete w-n ka apa write accses(mutq) uni 
ete x-n ka apa execute(katarel) accses(mutq) uni

other    group    others
rwx       rwx      rwx

directory -i hamar ete x permission-y drvacs e da yndameny nshanakum e vor ogtagorcsoxy karox e mutq gorcsel directory
drwxrwxr-x 2 ubuntu ubuntu 4096 Մար 24 19:49 pordsarkum



4. 
chmod  - chmod(change mode(poxel rejimy)

.1.
chmod -x pordsarkum 
chmod -x  nshanakum e bolori hamar ete es konkret chem nshum te um hamar em uzum hanem et permission-y

+ avelacnel
- hanel

owner(user), group, others - ays bareri arajin tarov naxanshum enq te u hamar enq uzum ayd popoxutyuny anenq 

u,g,o, a(all(bolory))

chmod u+r(user+read) file1  - user in trvec read permissionnery
chmod g-w(group-write) file1  - es xmbin patkanox cankacacs ogtagorcsox chi karoxana gri fayli mej bnakanabar ete ayd usery fayli owner-y chi
-rw-r--r-- 1 ubuntu ubuntu 9180 Մար 25 13:44 l6
chmod o+x file1  - otherneri hamar executable(katarvox,gorcsarkvox) darav
chmod a+r  - a(all), bolorin avelacnuma read permissiony

chmod u-r+wx file1
chmod ugo+r-w file1
chmod u+r file1; chmod g+w file1

.2.
chmod  600 file   -   rw- --- --- file

permission nery naev karox enq tal tverov

   erkuakan h.
0     000     ---
1     001     --x
2     010     -w-
3     011     -wx
4     100     r--
5     101     r-x
6     110     rw-
7     111     rwx




5.
/etc/passwd
user neri tvyalnery gtnvum en /etc/passwd faylum, voch te ogtagorcsoxnery anmijapes ayl informacian ayd ogtagorcsoxneri masin

ban ayn e vor csragrery linux-um evs karox en linel vorpes ogtagorcsoxner 
aysinqn ete duq uzum eq inch vor hatuk servis unenal inch vor csragir vory accses(mutq) e unenalu inch vor faylerin gorcsoxutyun ani ev ayln ev ayln da evs karox eq ditarkel ibrev csragir dra hamar stex csragrayin anunner evs ktesneq
orinak 
bin:x:2:2:bin:/bin:/usr/sbin/nologin


sa mer ogtagorcsoxn e
ubuntu:x:1000:1000:erik,,,:/home/ubuntu:/bin/bash

erku ketov bashanvum en hamapatasxanabar informacian vory verabervum e et ogtagorcsoxin
et informacian baxkacacs e hetevyal hatvacsneric

.1.
ubuntu:....
arajiny anvanvum e login name(mutqi anuny), aysinqn et ogtagorcsoxy inch anunov e login linum vorohetev login name-y u henc ogtagorcsoxi anuny karox en tarbervel iraric

.2.
ubuntu:x:....
erkrordy ays (x)-y patmakanoeren stex gtnvela ogtagorcsoxi passwordy,bayc hima aydpes chi ays x-y cuyc e talis vor ogtagorcsoxy password uni bayc ayn irakanum gtnvum e /etc/shadow faylum

ete ogtagorcsox stexcseq u et ogtsgorcsoxi passwordy hly drvacs chi aysinqn hly cheq hase ed qaylin sovorabar x-i texy linum e bacakanchakan nshan(!) aysinqn passwordy chka piti sahmanvi

.3.
ubuntu:x:1000:....
hajord tivy kochvum e UID(user identifier) aysinqn ogtagorcsoxi tvayin hamary
usernery baci iranc anunerov(login namerov) tarbervum en naev hamapatasxanabar uniq(ezaki) tverov, aysinqn voch mi erku user chen karoxana unenal nuyn id-in
mer usernery sksvum en 1000ic

.4.
ubuntu:x:1000:1000....
4rd texum aysinqn 2rd tivy da GID(group id)-n e,nuynpes inchpes fayli het asocacnum enq userid-in nuynkerp fayli het asocacvum e naev xumby aysinqn faylin karox e accses(mutq) unenal inch vor xumb u et xmbin patkanox usernery ev et xmbery mimyancic evs tarberakvum en id-nerov 
aysinqn stex inch vor imastov es xmbi id-in irenic nerkayacnum e hamarya nuyn ban inch vor userid-in uxaki en tarberutyamb vor es xmbi id-in share(kisvel)a exacs aysinqn kisvuma bolor en userneri het voronq et xmbum patkanum en

.5.
ubuntu:x:1000:1000:erik,,,
sa inch vor informaciaya ogtagorcsoxi masin ira amboxjakan anuny karoxa lini ira masin contaktayin tvyalner ev ayln, system adminerin harmara linum et informacian pahel es /etc/passwd faylum

.6.
ubuntu:x:1000:1000:erik,,,:/home/ubuntu....
hajordy useri home directoryin e aysinqn vortex e gtnvum et ogtagorcsoxi home directoryin 


.7.
ubuntu:x:1000:1000:erik,,,:/home/ubuntu:/bin/bash
ev verjiny login shale-na aysinqn ete usery uzuma ogtvi shall-ic vor csragirna da spasarkelu mer hamr by default da /bin/bash-na
vorosh csragreri depqum voronq ogtagorcsox en stex nerkayacvacs duq karox eq tesnel ayspisi artahaytutyun
/bin/false - sa nshanakuma vor et user-i hamar shall-i csragir goyutyun chuni
/usr/sbin/nologin - kam vorosh depqerum ete shall-ic nuynisk ogtvi login linelu kariq chi unena



6.
/etc/shadow
ame mi tox irenic nerkayacnuma mi useri passwordi masin informacia 

sudo vim /etc/shadow
ubuntu:$y$j9T$KnqY9EPCfSDHVdU/19Ge1.$yH/xfFWEzSGJEim13Km/ilERTCO/0tKo9wEPfVSG5R1:19801:0:99999:7:::


arajiny useri anuny erkrordy hamapatasxanabar ogtagorcsoxi passwordna bayc passwordy erbeq grete voch mi tex chi pahpanvum vorpes ayspes kochvacs plain text(parz teqst) ayl ogtagorcsvum e hatuk heshavorman algoritmner
$1$  - md5 algoritm
$2$  - Blowfish algoritm
$6$  - SHA-512 algoritm



7.
su  - su(substitute user(poxarinel ogtagorcsoxin) sa hnaravorutyunna talis poxel userin
su knuth - nshanakuma es poxum em es pahin ogtagorcsoxin, pordsum em noric login linel ibrev knuth user, sexmeluc heto uzuma password bayc im passwordy che ayl en useri um anunic uzumem sharunakel ashxatanqy

ctrl+d kam exit  - veradarnuma en userin vorov menq ashxatum einq

su - newuser??????????

8.
sudo  - sudo(superuser do(vorpes superuser katarir)), hraman vory linuxy asum e vor es gitem vor du admines ays hamkargi bayc du vorpes ogtagorcsox vorpes admin ches ogtagorcsum ays hamakargy
sa shat karevor nrbutyunna 
aysinqn chnayacs vor es ubuntui himnakan ohtagorcsoxy esem es myus ogtagorcsoxnerin esel stexcselem es evs ogtvum em es hamakargic ibrev sovorakan ogtagorcsox aysinqn es root usery chem ete es uzum em root usery linel kam (su root) vory vorosh hamakargerum by default algervuma, kam cankacacs hraman vory uzum eq katarel admini anunic cheq karoxanum katarel vorohetev duq sovorakan ogtagorcsoxi kargavichakum eq orinak (vim /etc/shadow) duq karox eq anel sudo vim /etc/shadow vory asuma vor duq vorpes superuserov eq uzum ays fayly bacel

ete usery sudo xmbum ka apa inqy karuma root-i anvan tak gorcsoxutyun ani 

ls -l /etc/shadow
-rw-r----- 1 root shadow 1465 Մար 19 12:55 /etc/shadow

$ groups
ubuntu adm cdrom sudo dip plugdev lpadmin lxd sambashare


erik@ubuntu:~/....$ chown ubuntu l6
chown: changing ownership of 'l6': Operation not permitted(gorcsoxutyuny, shahagorcsumy chi tuylatrvum)
sudo !!
sudo chown ubuntu l6
[sudo] password for erik: 
erik is not in the sudoers file.  This incident will be reported.
(Էրիկը sudoers ֆայլում չկա: Այս դեպքի մասին կտեղեկացվի:)

ete usery sudo groupum chka apa inqy chi kara sudo hramany ogtagorcsi

9.
chown  - chown(change owner(poxel sepakanatirojy)),voch miayn poxum e fayli ownerin ayl naev groupin
sudo chown knuth file1  - poxum e file1-i owner-in dardsnelov knuth
chown :adm file1  - poxum e file1-i group-in dardsnelov adm
chown knuth:adm file1 - dsax koxminy file1-i ownerina poxum aj koxminy file1-i group-in


10.
whoami - cuyc e talis te ove ayd pahin ogtagorcsoxy


11.
udduser, useradd  - user(ogtagorcsox) e avelacnum

adduser hramany asum e vor menak root-y aysinqn superusery kara et ani
adduser
adduser: Only root may add a user or group to the system.




ete taza user enq stexcsum  sudo useradd newuser  hramanov ira shell-y linuma sh-n
grep newuser /etc/passwd
newuser:x:1001:1001::/home/newuser:/bin/bash
vorpeszi poxenq ira shell-y anum enq 
sudo usermod --shell /bin/bash newuser




12.
addgroup, groupadd - group(xumb) e avelacnum

sudo addgroup imgroup
sudo addgroup imgroup
Adding group `imgroup' (GID 1003) ...
Done.

sudo adduser erik imgroup
[sudo] password for ubuntu: 
Sorry, try again.
[sudo] password for ubuntu: 
Adding user `erik' to group `imgroup' ...
Adding user erik to group imgroup
Done.

su erik

erik@ubuntu:~/....$ groups
erik imgroup



13.
script  - menq karoxanum enq stexcsel fayl vori mej grvacs klini hramanneri bazmutyun vory karoxa katari bashy ankax mer senc hertov havaqeluc aysinqn menq karox enq kombinacnel mi qani hramanner irar het

orinak menq stexcsum enq testscript anunov fayl(vim testscript)
ete es uzum ashxatacnem testscript-y ibrev csragir apa karoxenq asenq senc current directoryum gtnvox csragiry ashxatacra(./testscript) ashxatacra 
inchi em havaqum es current directory-ii nshany(./) vorovhetev ete uxaki grem testscript u enter tam sa shell-y haskanalu e vorpes hramani kam csragri anun, bayc mez sa petq cher mez petq er es mer gracsy vorpes bash-i csragir ashxatacnel aysinqn shell-i script vorpes
et csragrin vortex shell-i hramannern en tvarkvum aysinqn fayl vortex tvarkvacs en shell-i hramannery vor menq uzum enq bash-in poxancenq vor inqy katari nuyn dsev vonc menq havaqeinq himnakanum anvanum en shell script

./testscript ete sxmum enq asuma  permission denied nshanakuma execute(x) anelu permission chunenq  (chmod u+x testscript)

aysinqn ete menq unenq bazmativ gorcsoxutyunner vor alarum enq hertakanutyamb katarel sirun karox enq havaqel mi hat faylum harmarutyan hamar et fayli anuny karox enq dnel ynenc vor inqy avartvi .sh yndlaynumov vor ibrev inqy shell scripta(testscipt.sh) sa harmarutyan hamar, partadir chi u hamapatasxanabar es fayly darnuma scriptayin fayl vory menq execute(x) permission-y talov hnaravorutyun unenq ashxatacnenq 

cat testscript
echo hello 
echo barev
$((3+4))
echo hajox

./testdisk
hello
barev
./testscript: line 3: 7: command not found
hajox




